nge|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2022-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220611005456/https://www.fulbright.org.tw/zh-hant/2021-2022-fall-workshop-and-orientation-for-fulbright-u-s-grantees/}}</ref> 。來自臺灣的傑出學友含聲樂家[[申學庸|申學庸]]、雲門舞集創辦人[[林懷民|林懷民]]及作家[[齊邦媛|齊邦媛]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=名人堂|url=https://www.fulbright.org.tw/zh-hant/hall-of-fame/|access-date=2022-03-06|work=Fulbright Taiwan, Foundation for Scholarly Exchange|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2022-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220306095419/https://www.fulbright.org.tw/zh-hant/hall-of-fame/}}</ref>。每年全球共约7千5百人获选参与富布赖特项目<ref name="ffsb2017" /><ref name="ffsb2016">{{cite report|url=https://eca.state.gov/files/bureau/ffsb_annual_report_2016_gps__hi_res_20170824fl.pdf|title=2016 Annual Report|author=J. William Fulbright Foreign Scholarship Board|date=|publisher=United States Department of State|page=36|language=en-US|quote=|access-date={{dts|2019|10|15}}|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102034224/https://eca.state.gov/files/bureau/ffsb_annual_report_2016_gps__hi_res_20170824fl.pdf|archive-date=2020-11-02|work=Bureau of Educational and Cultural Affairs|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至2016财年，已有约38.7万人获选参与项目，包括140,844名美国公民和246,709名外国公民<ref name="ffsb2017"/>。参与者们在政府、科学、艺术、商业、慈善、教育和运动领域成就瞩目，截至2021年已有：<ref name="eca-notable"/>
